---
title: Steak Sammies with Spring Salad
description: No need to wait all day for that brisket! Slide on up to the table in just 20 minutes for tonight's steak sammies. These handhelds are complete with horseradish sauce and caramelized onions, while an elegant spring salad comes on the side.
